Bwana wangu natoa roho yangu na mwili 
kwako uliyenifia, Msalabani mtini.

3.Naamini ni wako, wako Yesu milele,
Niendapo popote wewe huniongoza, 
Unioshe daima, nisitekwe na zambi; 
nimepona kaabisa, Msalabani mtini.

4.Jua likawa giza, aliposulubiwa akalia mutini imekwisha,
Akafa ilikwisha kwa kweli, Alipotufilia watu wasamehewe,
Msalabani mtini.

Graham Sarah (1854-1889), 
On the cross of Calvary SLOW 4X4 


