Nikisema sina zambi nimekosea. 
Bwana wangu, ninakuomba neema yako ;      
Baba, nipatie furaha ya okovu wako.

5.Ni munyonge, mzaifu, siwezi lolote; 
Ninakuja kwako Bwana, niokoe x2

6.Unifunze kukupenda siku zote 
za maisha Yangu yote apa duniani x2   

