351.NGWINO YES’ UVUGANE N’UMUTIMA EB 
1.Ngwino Yes’ uvugane,           
N’ umutima wanjye: Maz’ umpumuriz’ uti: Ntabwo nagusize.
Nyugurur’ umutima, Nihutire kumva, Ijwi ryawe ry’ impuhwe,     
Nyuzuz’ ibyishimo.

Mbwiz’ ijwi ryongorera, Mbwiran’ urukundo; 
Ut’ uzanesh’ iteka, Ub’ umudendezo.
Vugana nanjy’ iteka, Mbwir’ ubudahwema,
Reka numv’ uk’ umbwira ngo: Sinaguhanye.

2. Yobora abana bawe, Uvugane nabo;
Ubuzuz’ ibyishimo,
Bige kugusenga. Mwami, 
Bitange rwose, Bakwiyegurire;
Tebuts’ ubwami bwawe, 
Twibanire nawe.

3. Ngwin’ uvugane natwe, Uduhishurire,
Iby’ imigambi yawe,
N’ inshingano yacu, Duhe kuguhimbaza, Tukubahirize,
Tujye tunezererwa gukor’ iby’ ushaka.

L.L Pickett, SPEAK TO MY SOUL, HP 144, IG 152,  NW 64 

