Bwana yu hai sitishwi na kesho,
Bwana yu hai sitaogopa;
Kwa maana yeye ananilinda,
Maisha yangu yanalindwa,
Maana yeye yu hai.

2.Jambo mzuri ni kwamba Yesu ananijali hakika; 
Jambo nzuri ni ile hakikisho, 
“Ninalindwa siku zote naye  Bwana”. 

Gloria Gaither, Because He lives, HFW 610, 
