(Ts) liwe musingi bora ndugu kwa unyumba wenu :/: 
Msamaha nao wajenga unyu mba, muwe mufano bora kwa jirani :/:
(S) Nasitwaomba Mungu awabariki, 
(Ts) Nasi twaomba Mungu awabariki, 
tabia zako dada ziwe kama zake Sara. 
(S) Imeandikwa kwamba utatii mume wako; 
(Ts): Nasi twaomba Mungu awabariki, 
tabia zako dada ziwe kama zake Sara.

Fr. ANATOLE     -     Hybride: ZOUK + SEBEN                   


