723.UMUGISHA W’IMANA NI WO NKENEYE   2/2
1.Umugisha w’ Imana ni wo nkeneye rwose 
Ndashaka kubatizwa muri wa Mwuka Wera 
Nejejwe mu mutima n’ amasezerano ye 
Yaransezeranije kump’ uwo Mwuka Wera.

2.Umugish’ atanga, umugish’ atanga, 
Uva mu buntu bwe ni nk’ amazi menshi, 
Arawunyuzuz’ ubu, abasha no kunkiza, 
Niyubahwe rwose n’ Umukiza wanjye.

3.Itorero ry’ Imana n’ iryo guhabw’ imvura, 
Isoko y’ umugisha dor’ iradudubiza; Twishimir’ 
ubugingo twahawe n’ Ihoraho, Haleluya, dushime, 
dushimir’ Umukiza!

4.Ibicu by’ agakiza bitugezeho rwose, 
Utwuzurize Man’ imitima yacu twese, 
Abera bawe bose bahore bezwa nawe Haleluya, 
dushime, dushimir’ Umukiza!

5.Ibicu by’ agakiza bitugezeho rwose Turagusaba, 
Mana, ubyohereze mw isi, Ibihumbi by’ abantu bihabw’ ako gakiza, 
Haleluya, dushime, dushimir’ Umukiza!

Henri J. Zelly, Like a mighty sea, Ny 150; 
